            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <section class="py-3 py-md-5 py-xl-8" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-12">
                    <h1 class="fs-2 mb-2 text-secondary text-uppercase">Welcome to our Canteen!</h1>
                    <h4 class=" mb-5">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" style="color: #a8a8a8;"></i> Our canteen provides a variety of freshly prepared meals throughout the day,
                        offering breakfast, lunch, and dinner options that cater to different tastes and dietary preferences.
                        Whether you're starting your day with a healthy breakfast, enjoying a fulfilling lunch, or winding
                        down with a hearty dinner, we focus on serving nutritious and delicious meals in a welcoming environment.
                        We’re committed to making every meal a satisfying experience.
                    </h4>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="row gy-3 gy-md-4 gy-lg-0">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                    <div class="card bg-light p-3 m-0">
                        <div class="row gy-3 gy-md-0 align-items-md-center">
                            <div class="col-md-5">
                                <img src="~/Assets/breakfast.jpeg" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="Why Choose Us?">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-7">
                                <div class="card-body p-0">
                                    <h2 class="card-title h4 mb-3 text-muted fw-bold">Breakfast : </h2>
                                    <p class="card-text lead">
                                        Start your day with a variety of fresh and nutritious options, including tasty idli( ଇଡ୍ଲି ),
                                        crispy bora, savory chop(ଆଳୁ), and fluffy puri(ପୁରୀ), all beautifully prepared and designed to
                                        give you the energy you need to tackle the day ahead.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                    <div class="card bg-light p-3 m-0">
                        <div class="row gy-3 gy-md-0 align-items-md-center">
                            <div class="col-md-5">
                                <img src="~/Assets/lunch.jpeg" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="Visionary Team">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-7">
                                <div class="card-body p-0">
                                    <h2 class="card-title h4 mb-3 text-muted fw-bold">Lunch : </h2>
                                    <p class="card-text lead">
                                        Enjoy a satisfying meal with delicious options like steamed rice, flavorful lentils ( ଡାଲି ),
                                        crispy fried vegetables ( ଭଜା ), tender chicken, savory mashed potatoes ( ଆଳୁ ଭର୍ତା ), fresh fish,
                                        crispy mixture, and a perfectly cooked egg to keep you energized.


                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div><div class="container mt-4">
            <div class="row gy-3 gy-md-4 gy-lg-0">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                    <div class="card bg-light p-3 m-0">
                        <div class="row gy-3 gy-md-0 align-items-md-center">
                            <div class="col-md-5">
                                <img src="~/Assets/dinner1.1.jpeg" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="Why Choose Us?">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-7">
                                <div class="card-body p-0">
                                    <h2 class="card-title h4 mb-3 text-muted fw-bold">Dinner : </h2>
                                    <p class="card-text lead">
                                        Enjoy a fulfilling meal with options like soft ruti, paired with hearty soybean curry,
                                        flavorful alu kasa, or delicious chakuli pitha. Complement your meal with steamed rice,
                                        comforting lentils (ବୁଟ ଡାଲି), and a tasty tadka to bring the flavors together.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
