                    <div class="card bg-light p-3 m-0">
                        <div class="row gy-3 gy-md-0 align-items-md-center">
                            <div class="col-md-5">
                                <img src="~/Assets/chicken biryani.jpeg" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="Visionary Team">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-7">
                                <div class="card-body p-0">
                                    <h2 class="card-title h4 mb-3 text-muted fw-bold">Extra : </h2>
                                    <p class="card-text lead">
                                        Enhance your meal with options like tender grilled chicken, flavorful biryani, or a freshly made egg omelette. Enjoy crispy fried fish, spicy chili gobi, rich paneer, or savory sautéed mushrooms for a satisfying and delicious addition to your meal(Extra Nonveg).
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
